00:24:01,103 --> 00:24:03,439
Semua pria di sekitar sini kecil.

296
00:24:04,740 --> 00:24:05,808
Kau lucu.

297
00:24:05,941 --> 00:24:07,875
Maksudku di luar penjara ini.

298
00:24:08,010 --> 00:24:08,910
Meski kau benar.

299
