Ya.

327
00:26:24,279 --> 00:26:25,614
Sudah kuduga.

328
00:26:27,282 --> 00:26:28,750
Nyonya Polk? Aku Dr. St.John.

329
00:26:28,884 --> 00:26:31,053
Kita bicara di telepon.
