330
00:26:31,186 --> 00:26:32,154
Tidak perlu repot mengisinya.

331
00:26:32,287 --> 00:26:34,356
Kami semua tahu siapa kau.

332
00:26:37,626 --> 00:26:39,661
Eileen, bisa bantu kami
membukakan pintunya?

333
00:26:39,795 --> 00:26:40,964
Terima kasih.

334
00:26:41,096 --> 00:26:43,265
Lewat sini.

335
00:26:44,867 --> 00:26:46,301
Mantelmu?

336
