Aku juga yatim piatu.

425
00:33:59,969 --> 00:34:01,670
Pamanku membesarkanku di Barat.

426
00:34:01,803 --> 00:34:04,206
Di mana matahari bersinar.

427
00:34:04,340 --> 00:34:07,709
