kau terlihat sangat familiar.

465
00:35:59,355 --> 00:36:01,057
Kau membintangi film?

466
00:36:01,190 --> 00:36:02,791
Hampir tidak. Aku bekerja
di penjara anak laki-laki.

467
00:36:02,925 --> 00:36:05,227
