01:27:24,839 --> 01:27:26,741
Eileen.

1013
01:27:29,345 --> 01:27:31,813
Tidurlah kembali, Ayah.

1014
01:27:33,349 --> 01:27:35,351
Mau ke mana?

1015
01:28:07,149 --> 01:28:09,919
Aku mungkin akan langsung berangkat.

1016
01:28:13,788 --> 01:28:15,723
Baiklah.

1017
01:28:18,860 --> 01:28:20,695
Selamat malam.

